’Ů@dcb142ba1786c745c59c95cc689eea558d78c76393c95c60c06458e9d51b18a3ŮÍTitle: title: polars cut
Path: Examples
Content:
Divide the column into three categories.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [-2, -1, 0, 1, 2] | polars into-df | polars cut [-1, 1] --labels ["a", "b", "c"]


